{"tid":381974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既人情味仲未絕跡","createTime":"2017-08-31T11:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T07:29:13.000Z","uid":55628,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3622076d5f21443c04ab51020f2505334ef5e8e0","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:00:38.000Z","msg":"話說，頭先勁撚大雨，我企喺有瓦遮頭既馬路邊，諗住等佢雨，點知愈落愈大，等左10～15分鐘左右，有個學生擔住把遮走過黎問我洗唔洗一齊行，嗰刻真係好感動，唔知有幾多年冇同非sell嘢既陌生人講野"},{"pid":"efbb230de03de7b8ee5bb854229ca0533f6987f4","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e084bbee80f549c442ad34f8b2ceb06cf3d5ca","tid":381974,"uid":67069,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"就係因為有人係自己最絕望既時候申出援手，所以我都會好想幫返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前有日我拎住個大紙袋，入面載住勁多野勁重，我拎既時候已經好辛苦，點知佢仲突然間爆開左d野跌晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果一刻真係無助到好想喊，身上面冇其他野載到亦都冇可能就咁用手拎返去，就係呢個moment有人遞左卷膠紙比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一比完我好快就走左，但我連佢個樣都未望到，我淨係記得自己係咁講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637cba1e6b840bf3c330a81c6df4fecfbc662f72","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人都可以講下啲好有人情味既經歷"},{"pid":"9b20006156ac46f68dd88d8904d5f4ed05005ec4","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係因為有人係自己最絕望既時候申出援手，所以我都會好想幫返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前有日我拎住個大紙袋，入面載住勁多野勁重，我拎既時候已經好辛苦，點知佢仲突然間爆開左d野跌晒出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果一刻真係無助到好想喊，身上面冇其他野載到亦都冇可能就咁用手拎返去，就係呢個moment有人遞左卷膠紙比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一比完我好快就走左，但我連佢個樣都未望到，我淨係記得自己係咁講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擔遮嗰個都係一過左馬路就走左，我都係不斷咁講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688803c6ea1aaaa37fd7ebacff1613b81487ba52","tid":381974,"uid":137766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:23:38.000Z","msg":"F.4果陣放飯陪我朋友買飯但我果日冇錢買，個店主知道我冇錢食野就免費送碗白粥比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d5db3d332106269cf52a084d1c2e9cdb135968","tid":381974,"uid":38194,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:13:56.000Z","msg":"你個銀包仲係咪度？"},{"pid":"4a27197a53e22832c7d700fc9e53ce78f5519b4f","tid":381974,"uid":67976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個銀包仲係咪度？</blockquote><br />\n係咪覺得自己好幽默？"},{"pid":"bddc7ffa57b7a5f96595de2b31b0737a19faad8c","tid":381974,"uid":55776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人會買旗"},{"pid":"990427db932afbac4cecd87a07bdfd3a848cd650","tid":381974,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個銀包仲係咪度？</blockquote><br />\n係咪覺得自己好幽默？</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，關心下你都唔得，仲學人講人情味"},{"pid":"2ac0b5e6d15c46e12711509354e1ec8972a06597","tid":381974,"uid":72567,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你個銀包仲係咪度？</blockquote><br />\n係咪覺得自己好幽默？</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，關心下你都唔得，仲學人講人情味</blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - 周周生菜 )"},{"pid":"7d56f542e82311a14d5117582fb345a55428ab39","tid":381974,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"你確定係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4822b2ad174e52cf406f228d9596c6d027c3e7b5","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個銀包仲係咪度？</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩少陣啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a926ace27b80b4f0219a89f8779f23872e86d3f0","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>F.4果陣放飯陪我朋友買飯但我果日冇錢買，個店主知道我冇錢食野就免費送碗白粥比我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢啲良心食肆真係越來越少見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0119e5e75182363d82b615138f9b73499a4d76","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有冇人會買旗</blockquote><br />\n之前有，但因為唔知啲機構會攞啲錢做咩，所以唔會下下買，就好似紅十字攞我哋啲血捐俾大陸人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3a62b130dcdc5a3c14472ace12159abdedcac6","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人，真係人，有體溫有實感<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1512b81513ccc8ea7c6a99d2b534b6750a1f6d21","tid":381974,"uid":141237,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:11:50.000Z","msg":"題外，有人情味未必係好人，要記住每個人都有黑暗一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依頭送碗粥俾你，果頭可能放左粒鼻屎落碗麵度俾第個客"},{"pid":"2f13d6655e6c8099da4bc3de60b585a5ba6af8b5","tid":381974,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5026f3f562c2e1c693bc9493ad3bea619291a3","tid":381974,"uid":28304,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"我本身就揸車送貨既<br />\n咁果日就黃雨<br />\n已經送到個人好頹<br />\n仲要得返半個鐘要荃灣趕去紅磡交貨<br />\n基本上係趕到仆街<br />\n你知我地d送貨仔係食物鏈底層<br />\n比保安恰都冇聲出咁<br />\n<br />\n好啦泊工廈拎貨<br />\n已經比個保安阿姐屌我泊位衰<br />\n又話唔夠貼又盛<br />\n攪到一頭煙<br />\n推架手推車埋車邊上貨<br />\n佢塊地又爛又唔平<br />\n我一路頂住架車仔一路上貨<br />\n好撚狼狽<br />\n突然有個保安叔叔走埋黎<br />\n好慈祥咁話幫我頂住架車<br />\n叫我放心上貨<br />\n又關心問我做咩咁趕<br />\n又叫我小心揸車<br />\n係咁問候我<br />\n即刻覺得人間有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我趕住走<br />\n好快咁道謝完就走左<br />\n如果唔係真係想留低請佢飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d98a8c796627b6e63bd6e143274971eceae9d5","tid":381974,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外，有人情味未必係好人，要記住每個人都有黑暗一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依頭送碗粥俾你，果頭可能放左粒鼻屎落碗麵度俾第個客</blockquote><br />\n屌，D大愛撚聽唔入耳㗎"},{"pid":"56c8c8c2e1921790a8128ec4d79b101dd84e380a","tid":381974,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個銀包仲係咪度？</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩少陣啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又一條儍仔"},{"pid":"e4b25590e46c024c8a921b85534e8f0af85d9053","tid":381974,"uid":96497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"睇完好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有無分享 想繼續睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da1ab97d3511b0bd551f1ef18382a3073f00b3d","tid":381974,"uid":90643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"前兩個星期天氣好熱，有個阿叔係路邊暈低，隔離幾個師奶好熱心咁扶佢埋一邊，一路call白車一路幫阿叔解暑同打氣，直到白車到左都有十幾分鐘。雖然連登成日笑師奶無文化，但其實最有人情味既亦係佢地。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有幫手扶"},{"pid":"68eecbed70f8bbe73d1d6a0803ce3f4a9717c782","tid":381974,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"咁你下次見到咁會唔會幫手"},{"pid":"95c44b8f24434199c679e3e26fef7701c33f620d","tid":381974,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外，有人情味未必係好人，要記住每個人都有黑暗一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依頭送碗粥俾你，果頭可能放左粒鼻屎落碗麵度俾第個客</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港畜是支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}